parameters.name: ForwardEntryId
parameters.description: The ID of the DNAT entry.

parameters.name: ForwardEntryName
parameters.description: The name of the DNAT entry. The name must be 2 to 128 characters in length. It cannot start with `http://` or `https://`.

parameters.name: HealthCheckPort
parameters.description: The probe port. The port must be within the internal port range. By default, this parameter is left empty.
